data.title: Indy Ball Report Podcast
data.text:
At the Indy Ball Report, we pride ourselves on being multi faceted and in order to do that we must provide more to you than just a weekly podcast. Thus, we created a YouTube channel. There you can find most of the video content we produce. However, we also believe that fans that visit our site deserve more. For that reason this section exists. Here you will find all our video content, including YouTube videos and bonus non-YouTube content.

indy ball out takes- general admission

Uploaded November 17, 2019

Audio from Episode XXXVII (37) 'Disposing of Mr.Bee' of the Indy Ball Report.

The first episode of the new series. Sometimes we go off the rails on funny and entertaining rants, that really don't fit in with flow of the show. So we are forced to cut them. However, you shouldn't be penalized for that. You can now see these out takes here, in our new series "Indy Ball Out Takes".

This episode we look at the guys longing for General Admission and why he is so important to baseball as a sport. Enjoy!
